11.结束一条语句 ：\c

12.退出mysql:exit

13.查看创建表的语句：
    mysql> show create table emp;
+-------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Table | Create Table                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
+-------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| emp   | CREATE TABLE `emp` (
  `EMPNO` int(4) NOT NULL,
  `ENAME` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `JOB` varchar(9) DEFAULT NULL,
  `MGR` int(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `HIREDATE` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `SAL` double(7,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `COMM` double(7,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DEPTNO` int(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`EMPNO`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 |
+-------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
展示创建emp表时使用的sql语句





**************************************【sql语句部分】************************************
    1.简单的查询语句（DQL语句）
        语法格式：
            select 字段名1，字段名2，字段名3.。。。。。from 表名；

       【注意】：任何一条sql语句已“;”结尾
       【注意】：sql语句不区分大小写
            mysql> select ENAME from emp;
            +--------+
            | ENAME  |
            +--------+
            | SMITH  |
            | ALLEN  |
            | WARD   |
            | JONES  |
            | MARTIN |
            | BLAKE  |
            | CLARK  |
            | SCOTT  |
            | KING   |
            | TURNER |
            | ADAMS  |
            | JAMES  |
            | FORD   |
            | MILLER |
            +--------+

       查询员工的年薪：
            mysql> select ename,sal *12 from emp;
            +--------+----------+
            | ename  | sal *12  |
            +--------+----------+
            | SMITH  |  9600.00 |
            | ALLEN  | 19200.00 |
            | WARD   | 15000.00 |
            | JONES  | 35700.00 |
            | MARTIN | 15000.00 |
            | BLAKE  | 34200.00 |
            | CLARK  | 29400.00 |
            | SCOTT  | 36000.00 |
            | KING   | 60000.00 |
            | TURNER | 18000.00 |
            | ADAMS  | 13200.00 |
            | JAMES  | 11400.00 |
            | FORD   | 36000.00 |
            | MILLER | 15600.00 |
            +--------+----------+
            字段可以参与数学运算

            给查询结果的列重命名：
            mysql> select ename,sal *12 as yearsal from emp;
            +--------+----------+
            | ename  | yearsal  |
            +--------+----------+
            | SMITH  |  9600.00 |
            | ALLEN  | 19200.00 |
            | WARD   | 15000.00 |
            | JONES  | 35700.00 |
            | MARTIN | 15000.00 |
            | BLAKE  | 34200.00 |
            | CLARK  | 29400.00 |
            | SCOTT  | 36000.00 |
            | KING   | 60000.00 |
            | TURNER | 18000.00 |
            | ADAMS  | 13200.00 |
            | JAMES  | 11400.00 |
            | FORD   | 36000.00 |
            | MILLER | 15600.00 |
            +--------+----------+
            别名有中文需要''
            mysql> select ename,sal *12 as '年薪' from emp;
            +--------+----------+
            | ename  | 年薪        |
            +--------+----------+
            | SMITH  |  9600.00 |
            | ALLEN  | 19200.00 |
            | WARD   | 15000.00 |
            | JONES  | 35700.00 |
            | MARTIN | 15000.00 |
            | BLAKE  | 34200.00 |
            | CLARK  | 29400.00 |
            | SCOTT  | 36000.00 |
            | KING   | 60000.00 |
            | TURNER | 18000.00 |
            | ADAMS  | 13200.00 |
            | JAMES  | 11400.00 |
            | FORD   | 36000.00 |
            | MILLER | 15600.00 |
            +--------+----------+
            【注意】：标准sql语句中要求字符串用''括起来。mysql支持”“，但是与数据库不支持

            as可以省略：mysql> select ename,sal *12 '年薪' from emp;

       查询全部字段：select * from emp;
        +-------+--------+-----------+------+------------+---------+---------+--------+
        | EMPNO | ENAME  | JOB       | MGR  | HIREDATE   | SAL     | COMM    | DEPTNO |
        +-------+--------+-----------+------+------------+---------+---------+--------+
        |  7369 | SMITH  | CLERK     | 7902 | 1980-12-17 |  800.00 |    NULL |     20 |
        |  7499 | ALLEN  | SALESMAN  | 7698 | 1981-02-20 | 1600.00 |  300.00 |     30 |
        |  7521 | WARD   | SALESMAN  | 7698 | 1981-02-22 | 1250.00 |  500.00 |     30 |
        |  7566 | JONES  | MANAGER   | 7839 | 1981-04-02 | 2975.00 |    NULL |     20 |
        |  7654 | MARTIN | SALESMAN  | 7698 | 1981-09-28 | 1250.00 | 1400.00 |     30 |
        |  7698 | BLAKE  | MANAGER   | 7839 | 1981-05-01 | 2850.00 |    NULL |     30 |
        |  7782 | CLARK  | MANAGER   | 7839 | 1981-06-09 | 2450.00 |    NULL |     10 |
        |  7788 | SCOTT  | ANALYST   | 7566 | 1987-04-19 | 3000.00 |    NULL |     20 |
        |  7839 | KING   | PRESIDENT | NULL | 1981-11-17 | 5000.00 |    NULL |     10 |
        |  7844 | TURNER | SALESMAN  | 7698 | 1981-09-08 | 1500.00 |    0.00 |     30 |
        |  7876 | ADAMS  | CLERK     | 7788 | 1987-05-23 | 1100.00 |    NULL |     20 |
        |  7900 | JAMES  | CLERK     | 7698 | 1981-12-03 |  950.00 |    NULL |     30 |
        |  7902 | FORD   | ANALYST   | 7566 | 1981-12-03 | 3000.00 |    NULL |     20 |
        |  7934 | MILLER | CLERK     | 7782 | 1982-01-23 | 1300.00 |    NULL |     10 |
        +-------+--------+-----------+------+------------+---------+---------+--------+
        实际开发中不建议使用*，效率低

    2.条件查询
        语法格式：
            select
                字段1，字段2，字段3.。。。。。
            from
                表名
            where
                条件；
        执行顺序：先from，再where，最后select

        查询工资等于5k的员工姓名：
            mysql> select
                -> ename
                -> from
                -> emp
                -> where
                -> sal=5000;
            +-------+
            | ename |
            +-------+
            | KING  |
            +-------+
        查询Smith的工资
            mysql> select sal from emp where ename=smith;
            ERROR 1054 (42S22): Unknown column 'smith' in 'where clause'
            mysql> select sal from emp where ename='smith';
            +--------+
            | sal    |
            +--------+
            | 800.00 |
            +--------+
            ename字段的type是varchar(10)是个字符串
        找出工资高于3k的员工
            mysql> select ename,sal from emp where sal>3000;
            +-------+---------+
            | ename | sal     |
            +-------+---------+
            | KING  | 5000.00 |
            +-------+---------+
        找出工资再1100-3000之间的员工
            mysql> select ename,sal from emp where sal>=1100 and sal<=3000;
            +--------+---------+
            | ename  | sal     |
            +--------+---------+
            | ALLEN  | 1600.00 |
            | WARD   | 1250.00 |
            | JONES  | 2975.00 |
            | MARTIN | 1250.00 |
            | BLAKE  | 2850.00 |
            | CLARK  | 2450.00 |
            | SCOTT  | 3000.00 |
            | TURNER | 1500.00 |
            | ADAMS  | 1100.00 |
            | FORD   | 3000.00 |
            | MILLER | 1300.00 |
            +--------+---------+
            mysql> select ename,sal from emp where sal between 1100 and 3000;